{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1638390/extras/Indies_Lies_Card_Battle_Steam_Storepage.gif?t=1734674904\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fresh take on Roguelike Deckbuilding Classics<br></li><li><strong>12 characters</strong>\u00a0from 4 classes to create your team<br></li><li>Over <strong>700 cards</strong>, <strong>160 Talents</strong>, <strong>90 enemies</strong>, and <strong>50 items</strong><br></li><li>Deckbuilding agility to <strong>replace cards</strong> or <strong>enhance them with <strong>Runes</strong><br></strong></li><li>High <strong>replay value</strong> due to procedural generation for each run<br></li><li>Paths with <strong>story events</strong> and <strong>mini-games</strong> entertainment<br></li><li><strong>Deep lore</strong> of Mekaa history and <strong>character story</strong></li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1638390/extras/Indies_Lies_Char_Steam_Storepage.gif?t=1734674904\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1638390/extras/feature_1_title_karma.png?t=1734674904\" /><br>Choose from <strong>12 characters</strong> to make the team. Each char has <strong>their own and class\u2019 cards, mechanics, and stats</strong>. While a hero sets up the main direction, it is your choice whom to invite to the party \u2014 debuffer, card spammer, or fire healer.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1638390/extras/feature_2_title.png?t=1734674904\" /><br><strong>Over 700 cards</strong> that can be combined with <strong>Runes</strong>, procedurally generated tree from <strong>160 Talents</strong>, and <strong>50 items</strong> \u2014 all at your hands to face over <strong>90 different enemies</strong>. Replace cards and adjust your deck on the go.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1638390/extras/feature_3_title.png?t=1734674904\" /><br>Continent Mekaa has a <strong>rich history</strong>, pieces of which you learn playing the Adventure mode. Each of the <strong>playable characters also has their own Story</strong> that lets you live through the most meaningful times of their lives.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1638390/extras/feature_4_title.png?t=1734674904\" /><br>Indies\u2019 Lies is a journey in the <strong>Dark Fantasy Steampunk</strong> world. You fight your way in the world on the verge between Medieval times and the industrial revolution. Complete <strong>Camp quests</strong>, play many <strong>mini-games</strong>, and discover <strong>on-map events</strong>  \u2014 each game will be different!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1638390/extras/Indies_Lies_Minigame_Steam_Storepage.gif?t=1734674904\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Collapse","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1638390/8add54f61c9efef1c659c744dd0fdc93066c8145.jpg"},{"name":"Talented","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1638390/710ab228039c8034566fa026d026d5b3dd97c1b7.jpg"},{"name":"Craftsmanship","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1638390/6d82846fb2e1fde80f135f0a273eaabb9f721847.jpg"},{"name":"Coalition","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1638390/4b3aac6ecae4351e37ef6e1916728853c18c5348.jpg"},{"name":"Witchcraft","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1638390/966c27ffefc04843267be0e0225065423ab99222.jpg"},{"name":"Mechanical Armour","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1638390/76cffc996f288c0545c6b673d576fe0bff59ae46.jpg"},{"name"